    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You combine three basic elements into a single attack, dealing 5d6 damage three times, each time from a different energy type from among the following: cold, earth, electric, fire, water and wind (Reflex halves, one save per element). Add the appropriate descriptors to the technique.<br><br>To deal damage of a certain type, you must have the appropriate elemental affinity (katon for fire, etc). An elementalist increases the damage dealt by their specialized element. Range is not affected.</p>\n\n\n\n",
